Author: David Balabon
Title: Moentum Token Pre-ICO: Currency Exchange Built On U. S. Patented Technology
Body: Moentum is at 70% of its pre-ICO phase.  Moentum Token will be financing SpotQuote LLC (a FINRA licensed firm) with the intention of launching a peer-to-peer Cryptocurrency Exchange and the first ever peer-to-peer U.S. Stock Exchange, respectively. The technology that makes us unique is backed by multiple US patents. We have a working product that we're ready to implement upon successful funding.  Proceeds at this juncture will go to expanding marketing infrastructure.  Check us out at https://www.moentum.com
